{
  "spec": {
    "title": "WebXR Plane Detection Module",
    "url": "https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "initiate-room-capture",
      "html": "When this method is invoked, the user agent MUST run the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>session</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this\">this</a></p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>promise</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-new-promise\" id=\"ref-for-a-new-promise\">a new Promise</a> in the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-realm\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-realm\">relevant realm</a> of <var>session</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsession-ended\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-ended\">ended</a></code> value of <var>session</var> is `true`, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#reject\" id=\"ref-for-reject\">reject</a> <var>promise</var> with a \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror①\">InvalidStateError</a></code>\" <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException\">DOMException</a></code> and return <var>promise</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrsession-room-capture-completed\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-room-capture-completed\">room capture completed</a> is `true`, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#reject\" id=\"ref-for-reject①\">reject</a> <var>promise</var> with a \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror②\">InvalidStateError</a></code>\" <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException①\">DOMException</a></code> and return <var>promise</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#plane-detection\" id=\"ref-for-plane-detection\">plane-detection</a> feature descriptor is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-contain\" id=\"ref-for-list-contain\">contained</a> in <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsession-xr-device\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-xr-device③\">XR device</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#dom-xrsession-enabledfeatures\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrsession-enabledfeatures\">list of enabled features</a> for <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsession-mode\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-mode\">mode</a>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#reject\" id=\"ref-for-reject②\">reject</a> <var>promise</var> with a \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notsupportederror\" id=\"ref-for-notsupportederror\">NotSupportedError</a></code>\" <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException②\">DOMException</a></code> and return <var>promise</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If the <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsession-xr-device\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-xr-device④\">XR device</a> doesn’t support manual capture or if the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsystem\" id=\"ref-for-xrsystem②\">XRSystem</a></code> determines that room capture isn’t needed:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrsession-room-capture-completed\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-room-capture-completed①\">room capture completed</a> to `true`.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#resolve\" id=\"ref-for-resolve\">Resolve</a> <var>promise</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Return <var>promise</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task\" id=\"ref-for-queue-a-task\">Queue a task</a> to perform the following steps:",
          "rationale": "invoke",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Invoke and wait for the result of <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsession-xr-device\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-xr-device⑤\">XR device</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xr-device-room-capture-method\" id=\"ref-for-xr-device-room-capture-method\">room capture method</a>, which is assigned to <var>result</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "Run the following steps:",
              "rationale": ".switch",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "operation": "switch",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "case": "If result is `true`:",
                      "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#resolve\" id=\"ref-for-resolve①\">Resolve</a> <var>promise</var></p>"
                    },
                    {
                      "case": "Otherwise:",
                      "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#reject\" id=\"ref-for-reject③\">reject</a> <var>promise</var> with an \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#operationerror\" id=\"ref-for-operationerror\">OperationError</a></code>\" <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException③\">DOMException</a></code></p>"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrsession-room-capture-completed\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-room-capture-completed②\">room capture completed</a> to `true`.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>promise</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "update-planes",
      "href": "https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#update-planes",
      "html": "In order to <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"update-planes\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">update planes</dfn> for <var>frame</var>, the user agent MUST run the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>session</var> be a <var>frame</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#dom-xrframe-session\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrframe-session\">session</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>device</var> be a <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsession-xr-device\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-xr-device⑥\">XR device</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#plane-detection\" id=\"ref-for-plane-detection①\">plane-detection</a> feature descriptor is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-contain\" id=\"ref-for-list-contain①\">contained</a> in <var>device</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#dom-xrsession-enabledfeatures\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrsession-enabledfeatures①\">list of enabled features</a> for <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrsession-mode\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-mode①\">mode</a>, abort these steps.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>trackedPlanes</var> be a result of calling into <var>device</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#native-plane-detection\" id=\"ref-for-native-plane-detection①\">native plane detection</a> capability to obtain tracked planes at <var>frame</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrframe-time\" id=\"ref-for-xrframe-time\">time</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "For each <var>native plane</var> in <var>trackedPlanes</var>, run:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If desired, treat the <var>native plane</var> as if it were not present in <var>trackedPlanes</var> and continue to the next entry. See <a href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#privacy-security\">§ 6 Privacy &amp; Security Considerations</a> for criteria that could be used to determine whether an entry should be ignored in this way.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes①\">set of tracked planes</a> contains an object <var>plane</var> that <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#correspond-to\" id=\"ref-for-correspond-to\">corresponds to</a> <var>native plane</var>, invoke <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#update-plane-object\" id=\"ref-for-update-plane-object\">update plane object</a> algorithm with <var>plane</var>, <var>native plane</var>, and <var>frame</var>, and continue to the next entry.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>plane</var> be the result of invoking the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#create-plane-object\" id=\"ref-for-create-plane-object\">create plane object</a> algorithm with <var>native plane</var> and <var>frame</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Add <var>plane</var> to <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes②\">set of tracked planes</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Remove each object in <var>session</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes③\">set of tracked planes</a> that was neither created nor updated during the invocation of this algorithm.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>frame</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrframe-detectedplanes\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrframe-detectedplanes①\">detectedPlanes</a></code> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes\" id=\"ref-for-xrsession-set-of-tracked-planes④\">set of tracked planes</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "create-plane-object",
      "href": "https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#create-plane-object",
      "html": "In order to <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-plane-object\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create plane object</dfn> from a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#native-plane-objects\" id=\"ref-for-native-plane-objects\">native plane object</a> <var>native plane</var> and <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrframe-interface\" id=\"ref-for-xrframe-interface③\">XRFrame</a></code> <var>frame</var>, the user agent MUST run the following steps:\n\n    \n    <p>A plane object, <var>result</var>, created in such way is said to <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"correspond-to\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">correspond to</dfn> the passed in native plane object <var>native plane</var>.</p>",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>result</var> be a new instance of <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrplane\" id=\"ref-for-xrplane⑦\">XRPlane</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>result</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrplane-native-entity\" id=\"ref-for-xrplane-native-entity\">native entity</a> to <var>native plane</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>result</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-planespace\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-planespace⑤\">planeSpace</a></code> to a new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrspace-interface\" id=\"ref-for-xrspace-interface③\">XRSpace</a></code> object created with <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrspace-session\" id=\"ref-for-xrspace-session\">session</a> set to <var>frame</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" data-refhint-key=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#dom-xrframe-session\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#dom-xrframe-session\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrframe-session①\">session</a></code> and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrspace-native-origin\" id=\"ref-for-xrspace-native-origin①\">native origin</a> set to track <var>native plane</var>’s native origin.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Invoke <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#update-plane-object\" id=\"ref-for-update-plane-object①\">update plane object</a> algorithm with <var>result</var>, <var>native plane</var>, and <var>frame</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>result</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "update-plane-object",
      "href": "https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#update-plane-object",
      "html": "In order to <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"update-plane-object\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">update plane object</dfn> <var>plane</var> from a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#native-plane-objects\" id=\"ref-for-native-plane-objects①\">native plane object</a> <var>native plane</var> and <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrframe-interface\" id=\"ref-for-xrframe-interface④\">XRFrame</a></code> <var>frame</var>, the user agent MUST run the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>plane</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#xrplane-frame\" id=\"ref-for-xrplane-frame\">frame</a> to <var>frame</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>native plane</var> is classified by the underlying system as vertical, set <var>plane</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-orientation\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-orientation①\">orientation</a></code> to <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplaneorientation-vertical\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplaneorientation-vertical②\">\"vertical\"</a></code>. Otherwise, if <var>native plane</var> is classified by the underlying system as horizontal, set <var>plane</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-orientation\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-orientation②\">orientation</a></code> to <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplaneorientation-horizontal\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplaneorientation-horizontal②\">\"horizontal\"</a></code>. Otherwise, set <var>plane</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-orientation\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-orientation③\">orientation</a></code> to <code>null</code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>plane</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-polygon\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-polygon①\">polygon</a></code> to the new array of vertices representing <var>native plane</var>’s polygon, performing all necessary conversions to account for differences in native plane polygon representation.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>plane</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-semanticlabel\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-semanticlabel①\">semanticLabel</a></code> to a new string with the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#semantic-label\" id=\"ref-for-semantic-label②\">semantic labels</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If desired, reduce the level of detail of the <var>plane</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-polygon\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-polygon②\">polygon</a></code> as described in <a href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#privacy-security\">§ 6 Privacy &amp; Security Considerations</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>plane</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/plane-detection/#dom-xrplane-lastchangedtime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-xrplane-lastchangedtime②\">lastChangedTime</a></code> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr/#xrframe-time\" id=\"ref-for-xrframe-time①\">time</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}